  "detailed_description": "\"Einheriar\" is a tower defense game where you must continuously collect coins to upgrade your warriors and equipment. Each warrior excels in different weapons, talents, and passive abilities.<br><br>You can use your imagination to create weapon combinations! For example, a bow can not only shoot arrows, but also shoot out other weapons as if they were arrows!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.poster.avif?t=1681371367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.webm?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.mp4?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Throwing out different weapons can cause different debuff to the monsters, such as allergies.<br>Also, make sure not to let the warriors use a weapon with a negative proficiency, as this will greatly increase your difficulty!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.poster.avif?t=1681371367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.webm?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.mp4?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game Content:<br>·6 classes: Archer, Mage, Spearman, Swordsman, Thrower, Idiot (without damage-causing weapon)<br>·Over 40 warriors<br>·Over 40 passive abilities<br>·Over 80 pieces of equipment and over 70 weapons<br>·Over 150 monsters<br>·7 debuffs: Bleeding, Stun, Burn, Freeze, Slow, Poison, Allergy.<br>·Over 150 levels and one final level.<br><br>Good luck!",
  "about_the_game": "\"Einheriar\" is a tower defense game where you must continuously collect coins to upgrade your warriors and equipment. Each warrior excels in different weapons, talents, and passive abilities.<br><br>You can use your imagination to create weapon combinations! For example, a bow can not only shoot arrows, but also shoot out other weapons as if they were arrows!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.poster.avif?t=1681371367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.webm?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/8a0260d87cece102624e150b6b8a057b.mp4?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Throwing out different weapons can cause different debuff to the monsters, such as allergies.<br>Also, make sure not to let the warriors use a weapon with a negative proficiency, as this will greatly increase your difficulty!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.poster.avif?t=1681371367\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.webm?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369740/extras/fdd4c183891b82899f647d09fe370f49.mp4?t=1681371367\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game Content:<br>·6 classes: Archer, Mage, Spearman, Swordsman, Thrower, Idiot (without damage-causing weapon)<br>·Over 40 warriors<br>·Over 40 passive abilities<br>·Over 80 pieces of equipment and over 70 weapons<br>·Over 150 monsters<br>·7 debuffs: Bleeding, Stun, Burn, Freeze, Slow, Poison, Allergy.<br>·Over 150 levels and one final level.<br><br>Good luck!",
